# Team Scheduler Dashboard

Full-stack app for managing team schedules, shifts, and work locations with role-based access.

## Tech Stack
- **Frontend**: React 18, Vite, TailwindCSS, React Big Calendar, Recharts (port 5173)
- **Backend**: Node.js, Express, Prisma ORM (port 3001)
- **Database**: PostgreSQL

## Data Models
- **User**: id, email, passwordHash, name, role (admin/employee), isActive
- **Shift**: id, name, startTime, endTime, isActive
- **Schedule**: Links users to shifts on dates (unique per user/date)
- **WorkStatus**: Daily status (office/home/leave) with leave types (full/first_half/second_half)

## Key Features
- JWT auth with 22-user limit
- Admin vs Employee role-based access
- Calendar/list views, shift management, bulk scheduling
- Work status tracking, reports with CSV export

