## Railway Deployment

### Backend Service
- Root Directory: `backend`
- Start: `npx prisma migrate deploy && npm start`
- Health check: `/health`
- Env vars: `DATABASE_URL`, `JWT_SECRET`

### Frontend Service
- Root Directory: `frontend`
- Start: `npm run preview -- --host 0.0.0.0 --port $PORT`
- Env vars: `VITE_API_URL` = `https://<backend-url>/api`

### Post-Deploy
Run `npm run db:seed` in backend for initial admin user (admin@example.com / admin123)

